# test_ifttt: Smoke test for useIFTTT in all three tiers
# Tests: mount trigger, timer trigger, key trigger, condition trigger

# Verify title
expect "IFTTT Test"

# Verify initial state
expect "Count: 0"
expect "RUNNING"

# Verify instructions
expect "Press SPACE to toggle pause"

# Note: This test uses useIFTTT hooks for:
# - mount: log on mount
# - timer:every:1000: increment count
# - key:44 (space): toggle paused state
# - condition: log when count > 5

# The count auto-increments via timer
# PAUSED state toggled via space key
